Content:
matthewauld 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/509] ported 'ansi gradient' command from nushell to engine-q
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/504] added a 'list' option to the ansi command
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/500] ported 'char' command from nushell to engine-q
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/494] ported 'ansi' command from nushell to engine-q
sholderbach 
