``Ctrl-D``
 exit in cli
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/507] made dialoguer completion abortable
jt 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/503] bumped some deps
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/501] fixed comment issue and shadowing issue
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/496] fixed a couple crlf issues
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/490] fixed bug in chained boolean typecheck
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/488] bumped to use latest git reedline
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/485] added better filepath completions
, and added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/484] ps still needs a delay to be accurate
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/482] made config default if broken
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/480] added in variable and sub-command completions
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/479] added in auto-cd if you pass just a directory
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/502] allowed flatshape (command line syntax) theming
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/489] allowed fg, bg, attributes to be set for all colors in color_config
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/486] allowed user to use hex colors in config
, and 
